Well, don't worry about it.

07:08.961 --> 07:11.123
A quick skin graft,
it'll be good as new (!)

07:11.123 --> 07:13.125
It's OK, it's OK. I'm such a klutz.

07:13.125 --> 07:16.529
No, no, no you're not. Not...really.

07:19.452 --> 07:21.574
Thanks.

07:21.574 --> 07:23.536
Yeah.

07:29.742 --> 07:31.784
Why didn't you say goodbye?

07:33.546 --> 07:35.588
